{"_path":"/trail/t013","_dir":"trail","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"水碓觀景公園","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":13,"category":"五股","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"水碓觀景公園"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水碓觀景公園"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公園簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水碓觀景公園於民國 88 年正式啟用，公園位於水碓路底，憲兵學校後方的水碓觀景公園，佔地 10.50 公頃的園地採斜坡式設計，配合坡度遍植花木，內有健康步道、自行車道、慢跑道，6 條長短不等的休閒步道及 7 座觀景涼亭，分別命名為凌霄、御風、覽勝等，提供民眾多樣化健康休閒設施，另有 2 條車道及 1 個可放 12 輛汽車與 10 部機車的停車場。引起周邊地區遊憩風潮，清晨的運動、午後的野餐、傍晚的夕陽、夜晚的萬家燈火、水碓觀景公園陪伴了許多人們的生活，近年來更加強其公園內的環境美化，栽植美麗的花兒及整齊劃一的灌木群。爬上公園最高點可觀賞、眺望大台北盆地景色，景色盡收眼底，還可以觀賞飛機降落的景象；夜間來此，景致更迷人。高速公路上南北往來的旅客可輕易地眺望公園精神字標「五股」、「WUGU」的造型字梯，晚上燈光透射，頗具特色，更感受到五股的親切與活力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自行開車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行開車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"開車 走明志路三段 / 107 縣道 11.6 公理，需 33 分鐘。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經過文桃路往新莊區，於新北大道七段/台 1 線 左轉。一小段後與明志路三段左轉進入 107 縣道"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"過與國道 1 號地下穿越道後，左轉登林路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停車：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在步道入口處，有停車區 但路非常窄。不建議進入"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"登林路上有收費停車場"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公共運輸"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共運輸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搭機場捷運至 A5 泰山站，轉乘 813 / 805 公車至明日世界站，再步行 1.1 公里 約 18 分鐘到達公園"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搭機場捷運至 A6 貴和站，轉乘 637 公車至憲兵學校站，再步行 1.10 公里 約 16 分鐘到達公園"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關介紹"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關介紹"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健行筆記 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hiking.biji.co/index.php?q=trail&act=detail&id=1454"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水碓觀景公園步道"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Youtube 2021/04/04 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gi5JDXD340c&t=160s"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" 五股水碓觀景公園、茂密樹林的輕鬆步道，台北近郊看夜景和飛機的好景點"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t013-01.jpeg","src":"/images/trail/t013-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"水碓觀景公園","depth":2,"text":"水碓觀景公園","children":[{"id":"公園簡介","depth":3,"text":"公園簡介"},{"id":"自行開車","depth":3,"text":"自行開車"},{"id":"公共運輸","depth":3,"text":"公共運輸"},{"id":"相關介紹","depth":3,"text":"相關介紹"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:trail:t013.md","_source":"content","_file":"trail/t013.md","_extension":"md"}